      "workflow": "discovery",
      "repo_path": "fixtures/dogfooding/llm-rag",
      "prompt": "/claude-tech-squad:discovery\nDesign a delivery slice for a new context-aware document retrieval feature in this RAG pipeline. The feature must include evaluation gates (RAGAS metrics) before shipping. Show explicit preflight and execution lines.",
